#include <iostream>
#include <fstream>
#include <string>
#include <conio.h>
#include <math.h>
using namespace std;
unsigned short a,b;
long long decTObin(unsigned int x){
long long value;
while (x != 0){
if (x%2 == 0) value = '0' + value;
else value = '1' + value;
x /= 2;
}
return value;
}
unsigned int binTOdec(long long x){
unsigned int value=0;
unsigned int i=0;
while (x != 0){
value += (x % 10) * pow(2,i);
++i;
x /= 10;
}
return value;
}
int main(){
freopen("doihedem.inp","r",stdin);
freopen("doihedem.out","w",stdout);
cin>>a>>b;
if (((a==2) && (b==2)) || ((a==10) && (b==10))){
cout<<"Error";
return 1;
}
if (a==2){
long long x;
cin>>x;
cout<<binTOdec(x);
}else{
unsigned int x;
cin>>x;
cout<<decTObin(x);
}
}
